This is an updated version of zonde306's mod "RF4 Chara Unlock".

Unlocks RF4 characters without needing a save file from RF4.

If the characters do not unlock on save load, try sleeping. You should receive the prompt telling you they will visit.

[img]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/davidthemaster30/RF5_RF4_Characters/1e4e6a927541eb1fde3b107867a41978ede0267b/Screenshot.png[/img]

[b]Install[/b]
[list]
[*]Install [url=https://builds.bepinex.dev/projects/bepinex_be]BepInEx BE[/url] version 647 or later (IL2CPP_x64) or install other base mod BepInEx already included (like [url=https://github.com/Lyall/RF5Fix]original RF5Fix v0.1.5 mod[/url] or my [url=https://github.com/davidthemaster30/RF5Fix]updated RF5Fix v0.2.0 mod[/url])[/*]
[*]Extract the contents of downloaded zip into [b]<GameDirectory>\BepInEx\plugins[/b][/*]
[/list]


[b]Uninstall[/b]
Remove the .dll file.

Code available here:
[url=https://github.com/davidthemaster30/RF5_RF4_Characters]https://github.com/davidthemaster30/RF5_RF4_Characters[/url]